{"id":125,"ayahs":[{"number":104,"arabic":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمْ تَعَالَوْا۟ إِلَىٰ مَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ وَإِلَى ٱلرَّسُولِ قَالُوا۟ حَسْبُنَا مَا وَجَدْنَا عَلَيْهِ ءَابَآءَنَآ ۚ أَوَلَوْ كَانَ ءَابَآؤُهُمْ لَا يَعْلَمُونَ شَيْـًۭٔا وَلَا يَهْتَدُونَ","translation":"for when they are told, \"Come unto that which God has bestowed from on high, and unto the Apostle\" - they answer, \"Enough for us is that which we found our forefathers believing in and doing.\" Why, even though their forefathers knew nothing, and were devoid of all guidance?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/773.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":72431,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72432,"position":2,"arabic":"قِيلَ","translation":"বলা হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72433,"position":3,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","translation":"উদ্দেশ্যে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72434,"position":4,"arabic":"تَعَالَوْا۟","translation":"\"তোমরা এসো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72435,"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"(তার) দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72436,"position":6,"arabic":"مَآ","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72437,"position":7,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","translation":"অবতীর্ণ করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72438,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72439,"position":9,"arabic":"وَإِلَى","translation":"ও দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72440,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلرَّسُولِ","translation":"রাসূলের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72441,"position":11,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72442,"position":12,"arabic":"حَسْبُنَا","translation":"\"আমাদের জন্য যথেষ্ট","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72443,"position":13,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"(তা সব) যা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72444,"position":14,"arabic":"وَجَدْنَا","translation":"আমরা পেয়েছি (অনুসরণ করতে)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72445,"position":15,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","translation":"উপর তার","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72446,"position":16,"arabic":"ءَابَآءَنَآ ۚ","translation":"বাপ-দাদাদেরকে আমাদের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72448,"position":17,"arabic":"أَوَلَوْ","translation":"(তাদেরকে বলো) তবে কি যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72449,"position":18,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72450,"position":19,"arabic":"ءَابَآؤُهُمْ","translation":"বাপ-দাদারা তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72451,"position":20,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72452,"position":21,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"জানতো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72453,"position":22,"arabic":"شَيْـًۭٔا","translation":"কিছুই","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72454,"position":23,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72455,"position":24,"arabic":"يَهْتَدُونَ","translation":"সঠিক পথে চলতো (তবুও অনুসরণ করবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_104_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72456,"position":25,"arabic":"١٠٤","translation":"(১০৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":105,"arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ عَلَيْكُمْ أَنفُسَكُمْ ۖ لَا يَضُرُّكُم مَّن ضَلَّ إِذَا ٱهْتَدَيْتُمْ ۚ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ مَرْجِعُكُمْ جَمِيعًۭا فَيُنَبِّئُكُم بِمَا كُنتُمْ تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"O you who have attained to faith! It is [but] for your own selves that you are responsible: those who go astray can do you no harm if you [yourselves] are on the right path. Unto God you all must return: and then He will make you [truly] understand all that you were doing [in life].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/774.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":72825,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72826,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72827,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72828,"position":4,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","translation":"উপর তোমাদের(দায়িত্ব)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72829,"position":5,"arabic":"أَنفُسَكُمْ ۖ","translation":"নিজেদের তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72831,"position":6,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72832,"position":7,"arabic":"يَضُرُّكُم","translation":"ক্ষতি করতে পারবে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72833,"position":8,"arabic":"مَّن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72834,"position":9,"arabic":"ضَلَّ","translation":"পথভ্রষ্ট হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72835,"position":10,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72836,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱهْتَدَيْتُمْ ۚ","translation":"সঠিক পথে থাকবে তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72838,"position":12,"arabic":"إِلَى","translation":"দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72839,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহরই","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72840,"position":14,"arabic":"مَرْجِعُكُمْ","translation":"প্রত্যাবর্তন হবে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72841,"position":15,"arabic":"جَمِيعًۭا","translation":"সবারই","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72842,"position":16,"arabic":"فَيُنَبِّئُكُم","translation":"তখন জানিয়ে দিবেন তিনি তোমাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72843,"position":17,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ বিষয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72844,"position":18,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা ছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72845,"position":19,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"তোমরা কাজ করতে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_105_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72846,"position":20,"arabic":"١٠٥","translation":"(১০৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":106,"arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ شَهَٰدَةُ بَيْنِكُمْ إِذَا حَضَرَ أَحَدَكُمُ ٱلْمَوْتُ حِينَ ٱلْوَصِيَّةِ ٱثْنَانِ ذَوَا عَدْلٍۢ مِّنكُمْ أَوْ ءَاخَرَانِ مِنْ غَيْرِكُمْ إِنْ أَنتُمْ ضَرَبْتُمْ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ فَأَصَٰبَتْكُم مُّصِيبَةُ ٱلْمَوْتِ ۚ تَحْبِسُونَهُمَا مِنۢ بَعْدِ ٱلصَّلَوٰةِ فَيُقْسِمَانِ بِٱللَّهِ إِنِ ٱرْتَبْتُمْ لَا نَشْتَرِى بِهِۦ ثَمَنًۭا وَلَوْ كَانَ ذَا قُرْبَىٰ ۙ وَلَا نَكْتُمُ شَهَٰدَةَ ٱللَّهِ إِنَّآ إِذًۭا لَّمِنَ ٱلْءَاثِمِينَ","translation":"O YOU who have attained to faith! Let there be witnesses to what you do when death approaches you and you are about to make bequests: two persons of probity from among your own people, or -if the pangs of death come upon you while you are travelling far from home -two other persons from [among people] other than your own. Take hold of the two after having prayed; and if you have any doubt in your mind, let each of them swear by God, \"We shall not sell this [our word] for any price, even though it were [for the sake of] a near kinsman; and neither shall we conceal aught of what we have witnessed before God -or else, may we indeed be counted among the sinful.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/775.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":73120,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73121,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73122,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছো (ওসীয়ত করতে চাইলে)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73123,"position":4,"arabic":"شَهَـٰدَةُ","translation":"সাক্ষী (রাখো)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73124,"position":5,"arabic":"بَيْنِكُمْ","translation":"মাঝে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73125,"position":6,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73126,"position":7,"arabic":"حَضَرَ","translation":"উপস্থিত হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73127,"position":8,"arabic":"أَحَدَكُمُ","translation":"তোমাদের কারও","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73128,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْتُ","translation":"মৃত্যু","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73129,"position":10,"arabic":"حِينَ","translation":"সময়","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73130,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْوَصِيَّةِ","translation":"ওসীয়তের (জোর উপদেশ)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73131,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱثْنَانِ","translation":"দু’জন","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73132,"position":13,"arabic":"ذَوَا","translation":"সম্পন্ন","audioUrl":"wbw/005_106_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":